data.description: Investors note, this house is under a lease contract for 1 year effective October 1st 2023. It comes with tenants and a signed lease. Welcome to this adorable colonial home that presents a rare opportunity to own a beautifully updated property with three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a non-conforming bedroom, a detached garage with a loft, and a host of modern amenities. From the remodeled bathrooms and kitchen to the new flooring, every detail has been carefully considered to provide comfort, style, and convenience. It sits on 3 lots  totaling .26 acres. Come and experience the timeless charm of this colonial gem!
